 22/1/17 . Did a rout march with pack up . Got letter this afternoon . Wrote some letter for we shall not be long now . 23/1/17 . I guess so . Gave in our blanket and march from Bazeiux to Becourt Camp ; about 12 mile . The coldest day I have ever known . Sent for a dixi of beer tonight , and it froze solid befor we could drink it . Made the bloke gnash their teeth a bit . The ground is freez hard tonight ; all the better finish mud ! 26/1/17 . Roll Blanket and move up about five mile and went into hut at Bazentim . Cover with moustach are busi shave them off now , for they were coat with ice today ; as their breath froze in the frosti air . Paid 20 Frs .
